    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Darkest Mine is a roguelite action-plateformer featuring some RPG elements and played in 20-minutes-long runs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/ea5fbb30eb5e9e0287f43812c7cecd54.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/ea5fbb30eb5e9e0287f43812c7cecd54.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/ea5fbb30eb5e9e0287f43812c7cecd54.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/fe4a49cc3c8a2955e1bc4105d74950be.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive down 5 depth levels made of 10 rooms each. You must clear a room entirely before progressing to the next one, until you reach the depth level's boss.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/b44ead67606943bb7c8c612658008a69.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/b44ead67606943bb7c8c612658008a69.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/b44ead67606943bb7c8c612658008a69.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/3571f4229e2824a9810224d284a51794.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every 3 rooms, you get a pick from more than 100 different abilities, each one affecting your gamleplay in a specific way. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/bc449c6eceb16738b656cc4961516181.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/bc449c6eceb16738b656cc4961516181.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/bc449c6eceb16738b656cc4961516181.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/46f1f1bdb9ee4d2031627a02708d2a21.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >4 weapons are available, providing 4 completely unique playstyles for your runs. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/fd6790b47ac001d6088d1775676db784.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/fd6790b47ac001d6088d1775676db784.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/fd6790b47ac001d6088d1775676db784.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/8a80f8af7cf53de325a638e6df08149f.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >With the gold nuggets you will collect through your runs, you can purchase permanent upgrades at the blacksmith </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.poster.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=114 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.webm?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/af5700397389ecfbe8ee4ef91d9e3cbe.mp4?t=1741849956\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/55cad006c93c3d46a178dc6ae129b9ad.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=88 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Local co-op and Steam Play Together are both available if you want to add a 2nd player to the run. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3172400/extras/b9cc5e29d40e28ea60483a32caafc63f.avif?t=1741849956\" width=610 height=120 /></span></p>",
